{"tid":764279,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【美國議息】聯儲局維持美息不變　下月幾乎肯定加息","createTime":"2018-08-01T23:19:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T23:50:53.000Z","uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"745cdf12110098c4b2a58ba03d629453abdb2cc9","tid":764279,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T23:19:34.000Z","msg":"美國聯儲局結束一連兩日議息會議，宣布利率不變，聯邦基金利率維持於1.75厘至2厘，符合市場預期。利率期貨顯示，下月會議加息機會達到100%。<br />\n<br />\n會後聲明重申漸進加息步伐，指美國經濟增長及勞動力市場持續強勁，貨幣政策立場仍然寬鬆，經濟所面臨的風險大致平衡。未來12個月整體通脹會接近2厘水平，儲局進一步加息的預期，將與經濟持續擴張、就業市場強勁和通脹目標強勁保持一致。<br />\n<br />\n是次八名儲局委員，一致投票支持維持美息不變。儲局年內仍有三次議息會議，分別為9月26日、11月8日及12月19日。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180802/58513356\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180802%2F58513356&d=iaCHxBfwVEno7mE5ptD2yB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=c928c7b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180802%2F58513356&h=6ba7340a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180802/58513356</a>"},{"pid":"b04de29970ac04e746e9ef58a9f9d5c10459c2cb","tid":764279,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T23:20:59.000Z","msg":"幾乎肯定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7f43e1d3c126111697a3f063ece93d7630a459","tid":764279,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T23:39:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.federalreserve.gov/monetarypolicy/bst_recenttrends.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.federalreserve.gov%2Fmonetarypolicy%2Fbst_recenttrends.htm&d=iaCHxBfwVEno7mE5ptD2yB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=cd1b1cfe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.federalreserve.gov/monetarypolicy/bst_recenttrends.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n縮表加速中，4.22萬億資產負債表"},{"pid":"1b76e42bf2c1b2